{"tid":1968622,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎放低自己內心嘅説話","createTime":"2020-04-11T19:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:26:13.000Z","uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"767e8db5b55eff7d7c4298ea55bc530afb0ea8db","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:45:03.000Z","msg":"係你地嘅眼中，我睇落係一個成日好搞笑<br />\n可以帶歡樂俾大家嘅人<br />\n但你會唔會想知<br />\n其實依啲都只係我演出嚟<br />\n只為咗刷存在感<br />\n當我一個人嘅時候<br />\n我唔覺得有人關心過我<br />\n我當你係我身邊重要嘅人<br />\n我先會俾你睇到我放負<br />\n希望你了解我內心嘅諗法<br />\n但到頭來，冇人想了解我真正諗啲咩<br />\n大家都只係有興趣見我帶住面具嘅一面"},{"pid":"010ef1e6dd3e6a6ad958a80e7e056e3d4fd9b47e","tid":1968622,"uid":322570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:50:13.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"5ffc5b79fa8b617bc98d8fc4a89c863c9d9a145c","tid":1968622,"uid":239525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:50:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"918a3bc88b8009e3d2ee41ab76bb9f7013ab3d70","tid":1968622,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T20:01:53.000Z","msg":"好肚餓 想食咖哩牛腩飯"},{"pid":"4fcdad45a3d72f94f5ae0144844f413c1e9edf57","tid":1968622,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T20:23:34.000Z","msg":"其實我真係好唔開心，好迷惘唔知點做，好想搵人傾下<br />\n<br />\n但身邊最close既朋友永遠咩都開玩笑玩玩下，同佢地講自己野永遠俾佢地串，話自己唔開心佢地都串我生活好好，唔會理我<br />\n<br />\n其他朋友又唔係好熟，唔想突然打擾人<br />\n<br />\n永遠都係我主動關心人，我都好想有人關心下我<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心就黎屈死"},{"pid":"6aa8a33b694b43179c6d5976fccc8df11cb8c43b","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ffc5b79fa8b617bc98d8fc4a89c863c9d9a145c","tid":1968622,"uid":239525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:50:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1cce023d8fa3dede739d08d124a9d523c77f3a","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"好辛苦<br />\n好空虛<br />\n冇乜真心朋友<br />\n冇另一伴<br />\n冇兄弟姊妹<br />\n冇人生目標<br />\n冇工<br />\n冇勇氣自殺"},{"pid":"77d2e0e58b25f8b34c22c42113513eb59ede4300","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T18:14:40.000Z","msg":"口是心非我最叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44f1e06f0e0e1f2f271930dfc99fc3999adcf15","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T19:07:19.000Z","msg":"點解又亂諗嘢呀"},{"pid":"660ee1bc809a824aeefc6a21ec850e5bfcf64a23","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:55:11.000Z","msg":"我唔知我可以點做<br />\n我咁做嘅話<br />\n我怕會俾壓力你<br />\n但如果我唔咁做<br />\n我怕我會失去你"},{"pid":"82ae7be7b48942638766089941917c38fca584fb","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:56:11.000Z","msg":"我好想喊<br />\n但係我喊唔出<br />\n定係我唔知應該笑定喊好"},{"pid":"6abde0d973e9c74030d62885e348ccaf575dcb46","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"成日扮到唔在意冇所謂<br />\n我好撚在意好撚有所謂呀"},{"pid":"4705399421e680e517820f20776ca70c436483c0","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:21:21.000Z","msg":"去囉<br />\nNothing to lose<br />\n因為我本身就係nothing<br />\n一無所值<br />\n又有啲咩可以輸"},{"pid":"97a693de2b1f87e943a851cccf9fff2e3c4c9b07","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:22:45.000Z","msg":"依個時候仲可以睇住自己寫嘅野係到苦笑<br />\n我都幾幽默"},{"pid":"fdaac2266364f2ed147453edb0f60f770c71fab9","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"又點<br />\n怪得邊個"},{"pid":"d47c035fe59aba72cbf65545defa925a215087c3","tid":1968622,"uid":319409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:11:39.000Z","msg"